Silver Bar: Buy this item to donate supplies to the "Rebuild Battleontown Fund". Does not take up a space in your inventory.
Silver Arena Coin: Keep this for use in the Arena Event and Pre-Event Merge Shops
Silver Dye: Use this dye with the Festive DoomKnight armor to make the Wintery DoomKnight armor.

Silver Key: This silver key has three bands on it - one gold, one silver, one bronze - and the alchemical symbol for sulphur is engraved on it. I wonder what it opens?
Silver Paragon Medal: Use this along with Legion Tokens to create pieces of the Draconic Paragon Plate armor set.
Simple Key: This simple iron key will grant you access to the Red Door in Hollowsoul Castle.
Silver Stack: Buy this item to donate supplies to the "Rebuild Battleontown Fund". Does not take up a space in your inventory.
Skill Tonic: Use to increase your dexterity by 16% for 10 minutes.
Skull: You'll need this to create the Skull top hats!
Skill Observed: Keep this item. You will use it in to complete the ArchPaladin quests.
Sky Pirate Dragon Soul: Keep this item to turn in for Legion Tokens!
SkyPirate Annhilator Recognition: Sell this token of the Skyguard's appreciation to reap your golden award for annihilating all those Sky Pirates!
Sky Locus: Your mystic parchment glows as you mark another location.
SkyPirate Map Piece X: The final piece of the map leading to the SkyGuard headquarters.
Slice of Cake (Misc): The Cake is NOT a lie!
Slimy Golden Pet: This pet will hatch once you merge a Golden Egg, 30 Emerald Flames, and a Golden Hammer from Cabdury in the Hatching Shop!
Slimy Platinum Pet: This pet will hatch once you merge a Platinum Egg, 30 Emerald Flames, and a Platinum hammer from Cabdury in the Hatching Shop!
Slugbutter Trophy: To the victor, goes the spoiled spoils.
Small Bag of Gold: Nice, you got a small bag of gold from the Luck Dragon! Sell this at any shop to get the gold, you lucky Hero, you!
Small Red Envelope: Who knows what this might contain!
Sluagh Bell: Jingle bells, Jangle bells… yep, those are Sluagh Bells all right. Use these in the Otzi War merge shop.
Smelly Golden Pet: This pet will hatch once you merge a Golden Egg, 50 Diamond Flames, and a Golden Hammer from Cabdury in the Hatching Shop!
Snow Globe Ribbon: The pink ribbon looks like it might be the one that tinsel has hidden here! Hurry and bring it back to her!

Soldier Badge: Use this Token to create gear from the firestorm merge shop
Solid Gold Coin: Although worth much less than chocolate, this coin would make a nice addition to any coin collection.
Solidified Soul: A Solidified soul used in Dage's Soul Forge to create Undead Legion Items.
Soul Essence: Reminiscences of souls tied together and forced to create a new thing. It's alive! (almost)

Souls of Gazeroth: Use this to create items in the /dreampalace.
Souls of Heresy: The Seven Circles are at war. To the victor go the spoils!
Space Dragon Balls: Not Spaceballs, or Dragon Ball, but Space Dragon Balls!
Spark of Hope: Gather all the hope you can and fight bravely against the oncoming destruction. Use these sparks of hope to transform the Sword of Hope into Kezeroth's Warhammers.
Space Jetsam: Keep ahold of this to make items in the Byro-Dax Merge shop.
Space Flotsam: Keep ahold of this to make items in the Byro-Dax Merge shop.
Spark of Life: It seems to emit various colors in response to your emotions.
Sparklebeam Elixir: Completely restores your mana, and gives you a healthy, lustrous glow!.
Sparrow's Blood: This potion grants 50% Evasion, 20% Haste, and a heal-over-time effect when consumed (potions must be equipped in order to be used from your Action Bar!).
Speed Bracer Bites: These fiber-rich light granola bites grant 40% additional Haste! When you've gotta go, you've gotta go!
